OL,3,CJersey residents support offshore wind
OL,4,Cfarm through public survey
OL,6,Fresidents support the idea of a wind
OL,7,Ffarm off the island's southwest coast,
OL,8,Fresults from a government survey have
OL,9,Frevealed.
OL,11,FMore than 70% of around 1,000 people
OL,12,Fwho shared their views responded
OL,13,Fpositively when asked how they felt
OL,14,Fabout the proposals at this early
OL,15,Fstage.
OL,17,FThe wind farm has the potential to be
OL,18,Fthe biggest infrastructure project
OL,19,Fever undertaken in the Channel Islands
OL,20,Fbut politicians appear divided on the
OL,21,Fnext steps.
