OL,3,CJersey residents support offshore wind
OL,4,Cfarm through public survey
OL,6,FThere are concerns over the wind farm
OL,7,Fbeing an eyesore and its impact on
OL,8,Fwildlife, but others believe it would
OL,9,Fbring energy security and boost the
OL,10,Fisland's economy .
OL,12,FA States debate is due to take place
OL,13,Fon the issue in April when politicians
OL,14,Fwill vote on whether they want to go
OL,15,Fforward with creating proposals - it
OL,16,Fis not a final decision on whether to
OL,17,Fbuild the wind farm as other
OL,18,Fstakeholders such as Guernsey need to
OL,19,Fbe consulted.
